t waiting for server handshake\\\" (frontend 日志中出现多个此类错误)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"类文件缺失 (ClassNotFoundException)，影响了日志功能。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"日志: \\\"java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: io.opencensus.contrib.logcorrelation.log4j2.OpenCensusTraceContextDataInjector\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n}\n```", "current_hypothesis": "`frontend` 是故障的根因，由于 RPC 超时影响其与后端服务的通信链"}
